# Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

### 1. What is LLM Studio?
LLM Studio is a Web3 project management tool designed to simplify, automate, and secure your blockchain initiatives through a unified platform.

### 2. Who can use LLM Studio?
Developers, startups, and enterprises engaged in Web3 projects looking for streamlined project management and automation solutions.

### 3. Does LLM Studio support multiple blockchains?
Yes, our roadmap includes multi-chain support with initial focus on major protocols. Current integrations cover top Web3 ecosystems.

### 4. How secure is the platform?
Security is a core pillar of LLM Studio. We implement best practices including end-to-end encryption, role-based access control, and regular audits.

### 5. Is there a free trial?
We offer a trial period for new users to explore core features before choosing their subscription plan.

### 6. How do I get started?
Sign up on our website, create your workspace, and connect your Web3 wallets and projects through the intuitive dashboard.

### 7. Are there tutorials or support resources?
Comprehensive documentation, video tutorials, and a responsive support team are available to assist users.

### 8. Can I integrate custom workflows?
Yes, LLM Studio supports automation and custom integrations to tailor workflows to your project needs.

### 9. Does the platform have an API?
An API is available for advanced integrations, with detailed documentation provided.

### 10. What kind of customer support is offered?
Priority support is provided to enterprise users, with standard support options available for all plans.

### 11. How often is the platform updated?
We release regular updates to introduce new features, performance improvements, and security enhancements.

### 12. Is my data private?
User data is confidential and managed under strict privacy policies to ensure proprietary information remains secure.

### 13. How does pricing work?
Pricing is subscription-based with tiers designed to accommodate individual developers to large teams.

### 14. Can I cancel my subscription?
Yes, subscriptions can be canceled at any time, with access continuing until the end of the billing period.

